Package idare.imagenode.Data.BasicDataTypes.MultiArrayData

This package contains the a Dataset specification for datasets with multiple sheets of containing multiple related sets of information.. * It is publicly accessible to allow its use in external plugins.
Author:
Thomas Pfau
